B.a4I=new A.P(B.a7c,["Omid Mirzaei","Senior Full-Stack Engineer","Flutter \xb7 Crypto \xb7 Web3 \xb7 Fintech",B.U1,B.XQ,"Senior Full-Stack Engineer with a mobile-first background and deep expertise in Flutter and Dart \u2014 7+ years across mobile apps, backend services, APIs and production fintech systems.\nMost recently at Block Labs, I work on Best Wallet, a multi-chain non-custodial crypto wallet with 100K+ active users: Flutter features across wallet, transactions, swaps and staking; Fireblocks MPC custody; Wirex card payments; backend contributions; and production debugging.\nBefore that, I spent four years shipping blockchain products at CoDeTech: CorePass (decentralised identity), XCB HODLER (official Core Blockchain wallet), and WebRTC-based communications.\nI use AI-assisted engineering workflows for architecture, implementation, testing and documentation \u2014 with careful validation for correctness and security. Fluent in English and Persian.\nOpen to senior full-stack, mobile-led and product-engineering roles in crypto, Web3, fintech and AI-enabled products. Based in Dubai, open to remote.",B.Zk,"Present",B.X6,B.XP,B.a4N,"Portfolio","Home","About","About Me","Experience","Projects","Resume","Download resume","Could not open the url","Language unknown"],t.yf)
